          <span>京公网安备110108020323137号</span>
          <span>京ICP备20018813号-3</span>
          <a href="#" class="hover:text-indigo-600 dark:hover:text-indigo-400">营业执照</a>
          <span>增值电信业务经营许可证:B2-20202418，A2.B1.B2-20202637</span>
          <span>网络文化经营许可证：京网文（2023）4872-140号</span>
        </div> -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
